# Development

## Toolchain

- Python {{ cookiecutter.python_version }}
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) for Python deps + virtualenv
- [just](https://just.systems/) for common scripts
{%- if cookiecutter.frontend != 'none' and cookiecutter.frontend != 'django-templates' %}
- Node 24+ and [pnpm](https://pnpm.io/) for the `frontend/` workspace
{%- endif %}
{%- if cookiecutter.container_setup != 'none' %}
- Docker 28+ with the `compose` plugin
{%- endif %}

## First run

```bash
git clone <this repo>
cd {{ cookiecutter.project_slug }}
uv sync                                       # creates .venv and installs everything
cp .env.example .env                          # never commit .env
{%- if cookiecutter.use_pre_commit %}
uv run pre-commit install                     # local quality gate
{%- endif %}
{%- if cookiecutter.container_setup != 'none' %}
docker compose -f compose.local.yml up        # Django on 8000, Mailpit on 8025
{%- else %}
just migrate
just serve
{%- endif %}
```

## Where things live

| Path | What |
| --- | --- |
| `config/settings/` | base.py + local.py + production.py + test.py |
| `apps/` | All project code (one app per domain concept) |
| `templates/` | Django templates, including allauth overrides |
| `static/` | Source CSS/JS/images |
| `tests/` | Cross-app fixtures (conftest.py) |
{%- if cookiecutter.container_setup != 'none' %}
| `compose/` | Dockerfiles + entrypoint scripts |
| `compose.local.yml` / `compose.production.yml` | Compose stacks |
{%- endif %}
| `docs/` | Architecture + deployment + security |

## Adding a new app

```bash
uv run python manage.py startapp myapp apps/myapp
# Then add "apps.myapp" to LOCAL_APPS in config/settings/base.py.
```

## Testing rules

1. **Tests ship with the change.** No untested PR merges.
2. **No mocks at the model layer.** Integration tests hit a real Postgres (via Compose or `pytest-postgresql`).
3. **Mutate one branch to confirm a test fails.** A test that can't fail isn't a test.
